---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-auto border-t border-paper-dark bg-paper-muted">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-10 md:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <div class="text-center md:text-left">
        <p class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-ink">皇汉学堂</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-ink-soft">素笺墨韵 · 中文历史与文化长文</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col md:items-end gap-1 text-sm text-ink-muted">
        <p>© {year} 了了子 · 版权所有</p>
        <p>本站由 Astro 静态构建</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
